      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in wonderful shape and has been super well-maintained, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner right away! It runs smoothly and looks great\u2014perfect for weekend trips or just getting around town. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
