    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving inline-six retains its factory individual throttle bodies and is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring optimal torsional rigidity. The chassis is balanced by an upgraded coilover system, providing sharp turn-in and minimal body roll. While the aesthetics reflect its status as a dedicated driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain remains robust with a functioning variable M differential lock. A true enthusiast's specimen ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
