    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Audi A6 Premium Plus that perfectly balances executive luxury with athletic performance. The exterior, finished in a deep Brilliant Black, retains a high-gloss luster; while you might find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway driving, the body is remarkably straight and free of any significant dings. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary. The Nougat Brown leather seats are supple, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster, and the genuine wood inlays remain vibrant and scratch-free. All technological features\u2014including the MMI Navigation plus, the 360-degree camera, and the crisp Bose Surround Sound system\u2014are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, backed by a comprehensive service history at authorized dealerships. We recently fitted a fresh set of premium all-season tires and performed a full fluid service, so it is truly turn-key and ready for the road. This car has been smoke-free, pet-free, and garage-kept, offering a driving experience that feels tight, responsive, and exceptionally refined.",
      "price": 34800.0,
